# Do not delete.
#
# `main.go` uses `//go:embed all:frontend/dist` — the embed pattern
# requires this directory to exist at compile time, even on a fresh
# checkout before `task build:frontend` has populated it. CI tests
# fail with "no matching files found" without this placeholder.
#
# Recreated automatically by the `ensureGitkeep` Vite plugin after
# every build (Vite's emptyOutDir wipes the directory clean).
